item.title: CVE-2019-1010112|2024-08-05T03:07:18.133Z -- oecms -- oecms
item.description: OECMS v4.3.R60321 and v4.3 later is affected by: Cross Site Request Forgery (CSRF). The impact is: The victim clicks on adding an administrator account. The component is: admincp.php. The attack vector is: network connectivity. The fixed version is: v4.3.
